37:42.961 --> 37:44.294
What it's like for you.

37:44.296 --> 37:47.130
And i do plan to have
all of those things.

37:47.132 --> 37:49.766
But, desiree,
what if you could, too?
Mm-mm.

37:49.768 --> 37:51.935
I've lost my chance.

37:51.937 --> 37:54.704
You don't know what chances
you might have left.

37:54.706 --> 37:57.407
And you never will,
if you do this.

37:57.409 --> 37:59.142
And neither will they.

38:01.380 --> 38:04.214
Penny...

38:16.094 --> 38:17.827
(moans)

38:19.064 --> 38:23.400
I am the astounding lizard girl.

38:25.637 --> 38:28.338
You get to live

38:28.340 --> 38:29.673
Only because i say so.

38:33.245 --> 38:36.980
But you come near me or mine

38:36.982 --> 38:40.350
Ever again...

38:40.352 --> 38:42.852
And i will kill you.

38:42.854 --> 38:44.354
(knife clatters on floor)

38:46.024 --> 38:47.357
Desiree:
Evie...

38:47.359 --> 38:49.759
Take him to the edge of camp

38:49.761 --> 38:51.795
And let him crawl home.

38:51.797 --> 38:54.597
(ripping sound, vince screams)

38:56.435 --> 38:58.268
Yes, doctor.

38:58.270 --> 39:02.172
I booked passage on
the<i> queen mary</i> out of new york.

39:02.174 --> 39:04.474
Open return.

39:04.476 --> 39:08.211
Doctor:
Mrs. Mott, i don't think
this is wise.

39:08.213 --> 39:10.747
I would recommend
temporary commitment.

39:12.017 --> 39:13.650
Oh, goodness, no.

39:13.652 --> 39:16.052
Dandy may seem durable,

39:16.054 --> 39:18.154
But he's actually quite fragile.

39:18.156 --> 39:19.522
Mrs. Mott...

39:19.524 --> 39:22.125
I fear for your safety.

39:24.162 --> 39:26.463
Thank you, doctor.

39:26.465 --> 39:29.299
We won't be needing
your services any longer.

39:33.472 --> 39:35.038
Dandy...

39:35.040 --> 39:36.740
You startled me.

39:36.742 --> 39:38.074
You think i'm
defective?

39:38.076 --> 39:40.643
Unbalanced?

39:40.645 --> 39:42.545
Fragile?

39:42.547 --> 39:45.148
I was only trying
to placate the doctor.

39:45.150 --> 39:47.917
We don't want him getting
proactive about your treatment.

39:47.919 --> 39:51.154
Well, if i am unbalanced,
it's your fault.

39:51.156 --> 39:55.425
Dora told me everything
when i was five.

39:55.427 --> 39:57.994
Your father was wiped out
by the crash of '29,

39:57.996 --> 40:01.164
And you would have done anything
to get back to a home like this.

40:01.166 --> 40:03.166
Even marrying
your second cousin.

40:05.036 --> 40:06.903
I loved your father.

40:06.905 --> 40:09.339
I was born of deadly sin.

40:09.341 --> 40:11.674
You knew what
father had done

40:11.676 --> 40:13.443
To those
little girls.

40:13.445 --> 40:15.879
You knew the risks

40:15.881 --> 40:18.948
Of breeding with your cousin.

40:18.950 --> 40:20.683
You're no better
than the roosevelts.

40:20.685 --> 40:23.086
How dare you say that name
in this house?

40:23.088 --> 40:25.021
I'm not going to europe.

40:25.023 --> 40:27.090
I'm not going anywhere with you.

40:28.860 --> 40:31.428
How can i possibly be
with a woman

40:31.430 --> 40:33.696
Who hates me so much?

40:36.435 --> 40:39.135
No, please, dandy...
(sobs)

40:39.137 --> 40:41.070
This is our
last chance.

40:41.072 --> 40:43.506
Can't you see that
you have a sickness?

40:47.446 --> 40:50.580
Your father wasn't
the love of my life.

40:50.582 --> 40:53.783
You were.

40:53.785 --> 40:55.985
From the second
you came out

40:55.987 --> 40:59.989
And looked at me with
that furrowed brow...

41:02.894 --> 41:05.562
...I loved all of you, dandy.

41:07.232 --> 41:10.366
Even the madness.

41:19.144 --> 41:23.079
But...

41:23.081 --> 41:26.082
I have no more love to give.

41:28.420 --> 41:30.920
You have tapped me out.

41:34.626 --> 41:35.925
You're right,
mother.

41:35.927 --> 41:37.494
I'm sorry

41:37.496 --> 41:39.529
I've caused you so much pain.

41:39.531 --> 41:42.832
It's time for this
madness to end.

41:42.834 --> 41:44.767
No, please, dandy.
Not this way.

41:46.438 --> 41:49.839
I can't go on
if you kill yourself.

41:49.841 --> 41:51.007
Okay.

42:06.324 --> 42:08.458
Oh...

42:08.460 --> 42:10.960
(shuddering inhale)

42:10.962 --> 42:13.263
(sighs)

42:23.041 --> 42:25.642
Maggie:
I thought you would have
sobered up by now.

42:27.712 --> 42:29.145
Why would i want to do that?

42:30.181 --> 42:31.881
Well, for one thing,

42:31.883 --> 42:33.816
You're supposed to be
in charge around here.

42:33.818 --> 42:35.218
Nothing makes sense.

42:35.220 --> 42:37.153
It's not making sense.

42:37.155 --> 42:38.988
The best way to honor ethel

42:38.990 --> 42:41.190
Is to take care
of business here.

42:41.192 --> 42:43.726
So we can leave.

42:43.728 --> 42:46.029
Start our own life.

42:46.031 --> 42:48.932
But you can't do that passed out
behind the ferris wheel

42:48.934 --> 42:52.168
Or wallowing over here.

42:52.170 --> 42:54.270
I mean, do you know
what almost happened last night?

42:54.272 --> 42:55.772
What's wrong with you?

42:57.342 --> 42:59.208
You sound like some
old schoolmarm.

42:59.210 --> 43:02.045
I'm the girl who fell in love
with a leader.

43:02.047 --> 43:03.580
A hero,
for christ sakes!

43:03.582 --> 43:05.682
Where is he?
Well, surprise!

43:05.684 --> 43:08.451
I can't just take my feelings
and roll 'em in a little ball

43:08.453 --> 43:10.086
And stuff 'em back inside!

43:10.088 --> 43:12.255
I'm not
general patton!

43:12.257 --> 43:13.590
Christ!

43:13.592 --> 43:15.191
Is that what
you want?

43:15.193 --> 43:17.794
'cause if that's the case,
then buzz off!

43:19.764 --> 43:22.131
That's not
what i said.

43:24.269 --> 43:26.135
Look...

43:26.137 --> 43:28.471
You need to eat something.

43:31.910 --> 43:33.309
Listen to me, jimmy.

43:33.311 --> 43:35.612
You didn't do
anything wrong.

43:35.614 --> 43:37.413
You're assuming that

43:37.415 --> 43:39.949
You could have saved
your mother, but...

43:39.951 --> 43:42.251
Just let the idea go, baby.

43:42.253 --> 43:44.787
You don't
understand anything.

43:46.558 --> 43:48.157
No.

43:48.159 --> 43:49.592
Give me!

43:49.594 --> 43:50.927
You shouldn't
burden yourself

43:50.929 --> 43:53.463
With the likes of me.

43:53.465 --> 43:54.964
Go have your beautiful life

43:54.966 --> 43:57.033
With someone else.

44:00.105 --> 44:02.105
(sniffs)

44:02.107 --> 44:04.273
All righty, then.

44:04.275 --> 44:06.042
Thanks for the clarity.

44:25.530 --> 44:28.031
You're still here?

44:30.268 --> 44:31.668
I am.

44:55.794 --> 44:58.094
(sobbing)

